## Working memory

`.ai/` is gitignored. Use it freely for scratch notes, ad-hoc scripts, intermediate outputs, and session handoffs. Never reference `.ai/` paths in committed files or docs.

## Secrets
{% if secrets == 'sops' %}
Secrets are managed with [SOPS](https://getsops.io/). Encrypted files are committed to the repo; you need the appropriate age or GPG key to decrypt them.

**Never write plaintext secrets to any file.** Use `sops <file>` to edit encrypted files. See [docs/operations.md](docs/operations.md) for key setup.
{% elif secrets == 'env-only' %}
Secrets are passed via environment variables. Copy `.env.example` to `.env` (gitignored) and fill in real values. **Never commit `.env`.**
{% else %}
No secrets management is configured. Credentials come from the deployment environment (CI secrets, etc.). Do not hardcode credentials.
{% endif %}
